{"tid":530841,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"青森樹冰遭噴簡體中文「生日快乐」 網友怒：別來日本","createTime":"2018-01-16T07:52:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-16T08:44:23.000Z","uid":75969,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"0df7176b5e7c95f81a8158f92e422e852f6b13d8","tid":530841,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T07:52:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cW8IDE-OemQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DcW8IDE-OemQ&d=X9IW%2BGPfmw1%2FZ%2F0ymGgNcP9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=1f5e96d0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cW8IDE-OemQ</a><br />\n<br />\n日本東北雪景享富盛名，青森縣八甲田山的樹冰是東北三大樹冰之一，每年冬季總吸引大批觀光客前往賞景、滑雪。不過並非所有人都懂得珍惜這樣的雪白美景，近日竟有遊客在樹冰上噴漆，寫上中文的「生日快樂」，引起許多日本網友不滿，怒吼這種沒公德心的人別再來日本。<br />\n<br />\n根據日本媒體「朝日電視網」報導，14日中午左右，有遊客通報八甲田纜車的山頂公園站附近遭噴字，約有4、5棵樹冰和地面上的積雪「遇害」，被人以粉紅色噴漆寫上中文和英文的「生日快樂」、「恭喜」等字。<br />\n<br />\n一名男性在現場目擊到有一男一女以噴字為背景拍照留念，不過似乎沒人看到噴漆的過程，因此不能確定他們是否就是破壞景觀的當事人。<br />\n<br />\n這些粉紅色的噴字隨後被八甲田纜車的工作人員清除掉，站方也呼籲觀光客不要惡作劇破壞樹冰。<br />\n<br />\n看到美麗的樹冰遭受到這種待遇，讓日本網友相當氣憤，有人留言痛罵「太沒常識，可以若無其事做出這種事有夠可恥」，也慶幸是在雪地，很快就能清理乾淨。由於「生日快樂」寫的是簡體中文，許多人直覺聯想到是中國大陸遊客寫的，狠批「國民素質太差」，但一名台灣網友解釋新加坡和馬來西亞都是用簡體字，因此不能斷定究竟是哪一國人幹的好事。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2018/01/16/99/4423494.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=1050&amp;exp=3600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2018%2F01%2F16%2F99%2F4423494.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D1050%26exp%3D3600&h=3e72747f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2018/01/16/99/4423490.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=1050&amp;exp=3600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2018%2F01%2F16%2F99%2F4423490.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D1050%26exp%3D3600&h=c8b5c70f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2018/01/16/99/4423491.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=1050&amp;exp=3600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2018%2F01%2F16%2F99%2F4423491.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D1050%26exp%3D3600&h=f5042bd3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/6812/2932018\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F6812%2F2932018&d=X9IW%2BGPfmw1%2FZ%2F0ymGgNcP9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=6bb0a0f7\" target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/6812/2932018</a>"},{"pid":"dd833c8e642841b9257176fffa56168d66103e48","tid":530841,"uid":57835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T07:54:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1d600fbe43c7bbc2a5e4a132802430c1df39a3f","tid":530841,"uid":147586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T08:06:38.000Z","msg":"這就是中國"},{"pid":"3c755be1f6268d106a38da8baf07e9523389230c","tid":530841,"uid":157197,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T08:07:56.000Z","msg":"垃圾民族去到邊都係黑人憎"},{"pid":"98d72de3de4432ba4fd2d6663cb53c4ab1396d16","tid":530841,"uid":23635,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T08:10:41.000Z","msg":"去日本留字，宣揚国威，我地識條鐵咩！"},{"pid":"b0e21392f8e9567557461b8412b08eaf3a4f900b","tid":530841,"uid":32782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-16T08:15:42.000Z","msg":"全世界得中國先會有呢隻粉紅色<br />\n想瀨都無得瀨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d399fb249f2f4591abbd881f0cfe71b25caa380","tid":530841,"uid":5686,"like":2,"disli